caption: I love this place. The B17 is one of the best sandwiches period. The staff is always great. The size of the sandwiches are well worth the price, plus Pepsi on tap is always a big upside.

I'm wishing the Brooklyn Bomber would have entered my life much sooner!  What a dynamite sandwich (egg salad, pastrami and mustard...who knew)!  I visited the airport location which is slightly more expensive but I don't care. It was the perfect sandwich for my quick layover.
Went for lunch this afternoon and had the Cajun turkey. It was absolutely delicious!!!! Bread was made in store and the Cajun sauce was so yummy! I will definitely be returning here!
Poor Service.  They got my order wrong.  There was one other person ordering so it's not like they were overwhelmed.  Disappointing because I really like the place.

This is certainly the best  Heidi's Deli in town!  I have been to a couple and not only do they know what they are talking about here they have hands down flat out just the best stuff the best meet the best flavour the most juicy the most tender the ingredients are just the best at this Heidi's I don't know why but this is what is!

The sandwiches here and service are so amazing. I will definitely return to heidi’s. My favorite sandwich is Hell’s Kitchen. They have the best egg salad sandwich I have ever had. Great job guys keep up the awesome work!!!!

I like this place.  It's efficient if you arrive no later than 11:15am for lunch.  Full loaves of various bread - carved upon your order to the sandwich thickness you desire.  Fresh ingredients, and plenty of choices.  Price is aligned with quality, and delicious.
